Detective, I have a culprit.

15:13.782 --> 15:15.958
The real man
who started that fire --

15:16.002 --> 15:19.353
my foreigner neighbor
who loves soccer!

15:19.396 --> 15:22.269
That's a photo of your neighbor
taking out the trash.

15:22.312 --> 15:24.532
Trust me,
he's a baaad banana.

15:24.575 --> 15:26.142
I know the neighbor
you're talking about.

15:26.186 --> 15:28.362
Bad banana, right?

15:28.405 --> 15:29.929
He doesn't fit
the profile.

15:29.972 --> 15:32.192
An arsonist is usually
low intelligence,

15:32.235 --> 15:34.585
completely socially inadequate,
a real loser.

15:34.629 --> 15:37.153
That's not true!

15:37.197 --> 15:39.982
I mean, our neighbor
is not like that at all.

15:40.026 --> 15:41.984
I agree.
Ah.

15:42.028 --> 15:44.595
Don't worry, Kevin.
We'll find the guy.

15:44.639 --> 15:46.858
We'll make it a priority.

15:46.902 --> 15:48.164
I promise.

15:48.208 --> 15:50.427
[ Laughter][Door opens, closes]

15:50.471 --> 15:51.951
